The Portfolio Committee on communications will today start the process of appointing new board members for SABC.Currently the board is headed by an interim committee which comprises of five board members, being Khanyisile Kweyama, John Matisson, Mathatha Tsedu, Febe Potgieter-Gqubule and Krish Naidoo.The vetting process of more than 500 existing executives and managers is now complete. comments